<div class="title">Don't Mix</div>
<div class="substance">MDMA (Ecstasy) & Amphetamines</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Dk_trippy&Exact=1">Dk_trippy</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Dk_trippy. "Don't Mix: An Experience with MDMA (Ecstasy) & Amphetamines (exp23144)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Feb 13, 2007. erowid.org/exp/23144</div>

<br/>



